00:38:36,280 --> 00:38:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] E to je slika kršćana

676
00:38:38,579 --> 00:38:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] koji se odluče

677
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] i koji ulože trud

678
00:38:43,619 --> 00:38:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] i koji dobe tu nagradu

679
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] i poslije zaborave

680
00:38:45,900 --> 00:38:46,659
[SPEAKER_00] na svu muku

681
00:38:46,659 --> 00:38:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] koja je bila potrebna

682
00:38:47,980 --> 00:38:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] i onog razočarenja

683
00:38:51,559 --> 00:38:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] i muke i boli

684
00:38:52,679 --> 00:38:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] koja ostaje na ovima

685
00:38:53,460 --> 00:38:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] koji se nisu odvažili na to.

686
00:38:54,980 --> 00:38:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ispravo se čini da ovi profitiraju.

687
00:38:58,000 --> 00:38:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

688
00:38:58,980 --> 00:39:00,280
[SPEAKER_00] za Božje stvari

689
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] je uvijek potrebno vrijeme.

690
00:39:01,920 --> 00:39:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se događa danas?

691
00:39:06,199 --> 00:39:07,739
[SPEAKER_00] Prebacuje se loptica.

692
00:39:07,739 --> 00:39:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] Lajci će reći

693
00:39:09,019 --> 00:39:09,880
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo opterečeni

694
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:10,820
[SPEAKER_00] svim živim djeca,

695
00:39:10,820 --> 00:39:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] roditeljski sastanci,

696
00:39:11,940 --> 00:39:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] posao.

697
00:39:12,599 --> 00:39:14,780
[SPEAKER_00] To je za svećenike i redovnice.

698
00:39:14,780 --> 00:39:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] Svećenici će reći,

699
00:39:16,219 --> 00:39:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] malo je svećenika,

700
00:39:17,159 --> 00:39:18,320
[SPEAKER_00] puno administracije,

701
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] puno posla.

702
00:39:19,260 --> 00:39:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] To je za zatvorene redove.

703
00:39:20,579 --> 00:39:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] Zatvorene redove će reći,

704
00:39:22,159 --> 00:39:23,639
[SPEAKER_00] treba raditi pekmez i siri.

705
00:39:23,639 --> 00:39:24,940
[SPEAKER_00] To je za pustinjaki.

706
00:39:24,940 --> 00:39:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] I često

707
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:27,900
[SPEAKER_00] se prebacuje ta loptica.

708
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

709
00:39:28,340 --> 00:39:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] moramo shvatiti hitnost tog poziva,

710
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] da smo svi pozdani na svetnost

711
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] i da možemo rast u mistici.

712
00:39:41,340 --> 00:39:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan Pavo II. kaže ovako,

713
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:45,139
[SPEAKER_00] da je veliki problem stav kršćana

714
00:39:45,139 --> 00:39:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] koji kažu

715
00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:47,820
[SPEAKER_00] da mi se domoči čistilišta.

716
00:39:47,820 --> 00:39:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže ovako,

717
00:39:49,039 --> 00:39:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] ili nas poneko od gorljivog odaziva

718
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] o našim trenutacim okolnostima

719
00:39:52,380 --> 00:39:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] odlači uvjerenje

720
00:39:53,239 --> 00:39:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne moramo baš sada

721
00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] previše usredotočiti,

722
00:39:55,780 --> 00:39:57,300
[SPEAKER_00] jer ćemo prije ili kasnije

723
00:39:57,300 --> 00:39:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] provesti čišćenje u čistilištu.

724
00:39:59,539 --> 00:40:00,820
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji nekoliko problema

725
00:40:00,820 --> 00:40:02,219
[SPEAKER_00] u ovakvom načinu razmišljanja.

726
00:40:02,219 --> 00:40:04,320
[SPEAKER_00] Istina je da ponekad ne postižemo

727
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:05,400
[SPEAKER_00] cilj za kojim težimo

728
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] i da je dobro imati pričuvno rješenje.

729
00:40:07,179 --> 00:40:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ako težimo doću raja

730
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] u trenutku svoje smrti

731
00:40:09,980 --> 00:40:10,699
[SPEAKER_00] i uistinu umremo

732
00:40:10,699 --> 00:40:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] u stanju prijateljstva s Kristom,

733
00:40:12,380 --> 00:40:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali se još nismo dovoljno preobrazili

734
00:40:14,519 --> 00:40:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] da bi smo bili spremni

735
00:40:15,599 --> 00:40:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] za gledanje Boga,

736
00:40:16,500 --> 00:40:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] čistilište je pravi blagoslov.

737
00:40:18,380 --> 00:40:20,340
[SPEAKER_00] No ako računamo na čistilište

738
00:40:20,340 --> 00:40:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] i promašimo,

739
00:40:21,079 --> 00:40:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] jasno je da ono baš i nije dobro

740
00:40:23,039 --> 00:40:24,659
[SPEAKER_00] pričuvno rješenje.

741
00:40:25,639 --> 00:40:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ljudi koji to kažu

742
00:40:27,159 --> 00:40:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] ne zna u šta je čistilište.

743
00:40:28,519 --> 00:40:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je jedna mističarka rekla

744
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] da je najblaža čistilišna kazna

745
00:40:33,539 --> 00:40:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] neusporedivo teža

746
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:37,219
[SPEAKER_00] od najteže i najmučnije muke

747
00:40:37,219 --> 00:40:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje na zemlji.

748
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] Marija Sima, mistična vidjelica,

749
00:40:42,079 --> 00:40:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom vidjenju dopustila

750
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] da duša iz čistilište

751
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] samo dotakne sa vatrenim prstom

752
00:40:48,900 --> 00:40:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] koje bi cijela osoba

753
00:40:50,059 --> 00:40:51,480
[SPEAKER_00] njene bila u vatri čišćenja

754
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] i ostala je fizički u krevetu

755
00:40:53,539 --> 00:40:54,280
[SPEAKER_00] tjedan dana.

756
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:56,219
[SPEAKER_00] Samo tog dodira koja je imala

757
00:40:56,219 --> 00:40:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] u mističnoj viziji.

758
00:40:57,119 --> 00:41:00,679
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ljudi koji to kažu

759
00:41:00,679 --> 00:41:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] nisu svjesni šta je čistilište.

760
00:41:02,340 --> 00:41:03,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi Bog dopustio da naši

761
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] često pokojnji nas kroz nove

762
00:41:05,599 --> 00:41:06,679
[SPEAKER_00] opominju iz čistilišta

763
00:41:06,679 --> 00:41:08,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa da za njih uplačujemo mise.

764
00:41:08,199 --> 00:41:10,219
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, Bog kao dobar otac

765
00:41:10,219 --> 00:41:11,860
[SPEAKER_00] nudi tu svetost

766
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] koja je teška, ali nije pre teška

767
00:41:13,940 --> 00:41:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] već ovdje na zemlji.

768
00:41:15,159 --> 00:41:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] I nudi pravilo postupnosti.

769
00:41:17,199 --> 00:41:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] Stvar po stvar.

770
00:41:18,880 --> 00:41:22,239
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoj napast sve svoje mane odjednom.

771
00:41:22,340 --> 00:41:24,260
[SPEAKER_00] odluči danas da će se ohvatiti

772
00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] sa jednim svojim porokom.

773
00:41:25,400 --> 00:41:27,559
[SPEAKER_00] Psovka, cigarete,

774
00:41:27,559 --> 00:41:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] hladionica,

775
00:41:28,699 --> 00:41:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] svađa sa mužem,

776
00:41:30,699 --> 00:41:31,300
[SPEAKER_00] sa ženom.

777
00:41:31,300 --> 00:41:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Al, napadni tu stvar.

778
00:41:33,420 --> 00:41:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] I kad jednu stvar pobjediš,

779
00:41:34,980 --> 00:41:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] pa osjetit ćeš pole,

780
00:41:36,300 --> 00:41:37,179
[SPEAKER_00] gledaj, ja to mogu.

781
00:41:37,179 --> 00:41:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog će ti dat vjeru i snagu

782
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] da uđeš u nešto drugo,

783
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] još jače.

784
00:41:41,699 --> 00:41:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] I tako se raste.

785
00:41:43,019 --> 00:41:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] Glavni problem je što se mi

786
00:41:45,639 --> 00:41:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] obeshrabrimo kad smo šokirani

787
00:41:47,940 --> 00:41:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] sa svojom grešnosti.

788
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte biti šokirani.

789
00:41:50,019 --> 00:41:51,440
[SPEAKER_00] Bog vas koristi.

790
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] Bog vas koristi ovakve

791
00:41:53,739 --> 00:41:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] i može vas koristiti još puno više.

792
00:41:57,619 --> 00:42:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] Božjoj milosti

793
00:42:00,559 --> 00:42:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] da blagoslovi vaš trud

794
00:42:02,860 --> 00:42:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] i da učini od vas sveci.

795
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže pisac poslanice Hebrajima

796
00:42:10,599 --> 00:42:11,860
[SPEAKER_00] oko posvećenja

797
00:42:11,860 --> 00:42:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] bez kojeg nitko neće vidjeti gospodina.

798
00:42:14,420 --> 00:42:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] Posvećenje je nužno

799
00:42:15,900 --> 00:42:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] da bi vidjeli gospodina.

800
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:23,659
[SPEAKER_00] Proćemo kratko pregled.

801
00:42:23,659 --> 00:42:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] Sad da vidimo šta nas čeka na putovanju

802
00:42:26,340 --> 00:42:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] kroz tri faze

803
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:29,860
[SPEAKER_00] duhovnog života.

804
00:42:29,860 --> 00:42:30,920
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo

805
00:42:30,920 --> 00:42:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] znači

806
00:42:32,780 --> 00:42:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] proću, proću, kratko, tri faze

807
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćemo vidjeti po svecima.

808
00:42:36,139 --> 00:42:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] U duhovnosti se možete nalaziti

809
00:42:38,579 --> 00:42:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] u tri faze.

810
00:42:40,139 --> 00:42:41,679
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo je faza čišćenja.

811
00:42:41,679 --> 00:42:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] Fazu čišćenja karakteriziraju

812
00:42:43,920 --> 00:42:46,099
[SPEAKER_00] ove odrednici.

813
00:42:46,099 --> 00:42:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] Obračenje,

814
00:42:48,860 --> 00:42:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] odbacivanje grijeha,

815
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] dovođenje života

816
00:42:52,340 --> 00:42:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] u sklad s moralnim zakonom,

817
00:42:54,940 --> 00:42:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] razvijanje molitvenih navika

818
00:42:56,639 --> 00:42:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] i obavljanje pobožnosti

819
00:42:59,019 --> 00:43:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] te relativno postojno življenje

820
00:43:01,300 --> 00:43:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] unutar crkve.

821
00:43:02,119 --> 00:43:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znači čovjek se odluče obratiti,

822
00:43:04,099 --> 00:43:05,559
[SPEAKER_00] počinje se boriti sa teškim

823
00:43:05,559 --> 00:43:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] smrtnim grijesima,

824
00:43:06,539 --> 00:43:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] njih odbacuje svog života,

825
00:43:08,260 --> 00:43:10,139
[SPEAKER_00] dovede život u red

826
00:43:10,139 --> 00:43:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] i počinje uglavnom

827
00:43:11,079 --> 00:43:12,820
[SPEAKER_00] molitvene neke nakane

828
00:43:12,820 --> 00:43:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] koje su više usmene.

829
00:43:14,960 --> 00:43:16,360
[SPEAKER_00] Znači počinje moliti krunicu,

830
00:43:16,360 --> 00:43:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi na svetu misu

831
00:43:17,460 --> 00:43:19,059
[SPEAKER_00] i relativno postojno življenje

832
00:43:19,059 --> 00:43:19,840
[SPEAKER_00] unutar crkve.

833
00:43:19,840 --> 00:43:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] Nekdje se ustabilije

834
00:43:20,980 --> 00:43:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] u nekoj zajednici.

835
00:43:22,019 --> 00:43:25,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ove faze,

836
00:43:25,179 --> 00:43:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] kod Ivana od Križa

837
00:43:26,860 --> 00:43:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] je to jedna faza,

838
00:43:27,679 --> 00:43:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] kod Sv. Tereze Zavilske

839
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] to su tri faze,

840
00:43:29,900 --> 00:43:30,800
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno tri etape

841
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] ili tri odaje

842
00:43:31,579 --> 00:43:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] u njenom zamku duše.

843
00:43:34,039 --> 00:43:35,139
[SPEAKER_00] Etapa prosvjetljenja

844
00:43:35,139 --> 00:43:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] je put daljnjeg rasta.

845
00:43:36,400 --> 00:43:37,639
[SPEAKER_00] Oni koji se učvrste

846
00:43:37,639 --> 00:43:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] u čišćenju

847
00:43:38,340 --> 00:43:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] čeka faza prosvjetljenja.

848
00:43:40,739 --> 00:43:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže

849
00:43:41,659 --> 00:43:42,820
[SPEAKER_00] dublja molitva,

850
00:43:42,820 --> 00:43:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] rastu krepostima,

851
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:45,860
[SPEAKER_00] produbljenje ljubavi

852
00:43:45,860 --> 00:43:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] prema bližnjemu,

853
00:43:46,820 --> 00:43:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] veća moralna stabilnost,

854
00:43:48,880 --> 00:43:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] potpunije predanje

855
00:43:50,420 --> 00:43:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kristovu gospodstvu,

856
00:43:51,460 --> 00:43:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] veća nenavezanost,

857
00:43:52,739 --> 00:43:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] praćenje različitim

858
00:43:54,199 --> 00:43:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] kušnjama i čišćenjima,

859
00:43:55,420 --> 00:43:56,840
[SPEAKER_00] ali velikim utjehama

860
00:43:56,840 --> 00:43:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] i blagoslovima.

861
00:43:58,099 --> 00:44:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] I tu se već počinju javljati

862
00:44:00,619 --> 00:44:02,280
[SPEAKER_00] mistični fenomeni kod osoba.

863
00:44:02,539 --> 00:44:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, molitva postoje dublja,

864
00:44:03,960 --> 00:44:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] javlja se istinska ljubav

865
00:44:05,159 --> 00:44:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] prema bližnjemu,

866
00:44:06,079 --> 00:44:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] žar za služenjem

867
00:44:07,599 --> 00:44:09,880
[SPEAKER_00] i veća nenavezanost

868
00:44:09,880 --> 00:44:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] i duša stvarno počne

869
00:44:11,079 --> 00:44:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] čeznut za Bogom.

870
00:44:12,099 --> 00:44:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] U prvoj fazi čišćenja

871
00:44:13,659 --> 00:44:15,260
[SPEAKER_00] se ti moraš prisiljavati još.

872
00:44:15,260 --> 00:44:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] Moram otići na misu,

873
00:44:16,519 --> 00:44:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] imam napast i kad trebam moliti.

874
00:44:19,039 --> 00:44:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] A u ovoj fazi,

875
00:44:19,880 --> 00:44:21,320
[SPEAKER_00] već ako ne odeš na misu,

876
00:44:21,320 --> 00:44:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] ako nisi ništa izmolio kroz dan,

877
00:44:22,920 --> 00:44:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] osjećaš da ti to jako fali.

878
00:44:24,739 --> 00:44:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] I osjećaš radost

879
00:44:26,039 --> 00:44:27,780
[SPEAKER_00] kad ti to možeš nadoknaditi.

880
00:44:28,739 --> 00:44:29,820
[SPEAKER_00] I put sjedinjenja

881
00:44:29,820 --> 00:44:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] je etapa dubokog postojanog

882
00:44:32,619 --> 00:44:33,739
[SPEAKER_00] sjedinjenja s Bogom.

