[SPEAKER_00] I ne ide.

1522
00:59:11,559 --> 00:59:15,460
[SPEAKER_00] Skriva se ispovijeda po klupama

1523
00:59:15,460 --> 00:59:16,800
[SPEAKER_00] ili je zabranjeno djelovanje

1524
00:59:16,800 --> 00:59:18,059
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže ovako.

1525
00:59:18,059 --> 00:59:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] Njegova jedna suradnica,

1526
00:59:20,199 --> 00:59:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] najbliža koja je bila s njim

1527
00:59:21,340 --> 00:59:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] u njegovim početcima,

1528
00:59:22,360 --> 00:59:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] opisuje

1529
00:59:23,440 --> 00:59:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] njegovu nadnaravnu nadu.

1530
00:59:27,119 --> 00:59:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, Sveti Hozee Marija je skriva

1531
00:59:29,000 --> 00:59:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] bio veliki zagovaratelj nade.

1532
00:59:30,659 --> 00:59:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] To se može vidjeti u pisanom izvješću

1533
00:59:32,980 --> 00:59:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] sa sastancima sa članicama

1534
00:59:34,500 --> 00:59:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] ženskog ogranka Opus Deja

1535
00:59:36,000 --> 00:59:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] od držnog 42. u Madridu.

1536
00:59:38,340 --> 00:59:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] Eskriva ovaj sastanak započeo

1537
00:59:40,940 --> 00:59:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] tako što je skicirao

1538
00:59:42,139 --> 00:59:43,840
[SPEAKER_00] mnoštvo ambicioznih projekata,

1539
00:59:43,840 --> 00:59:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] koji su imali za cilj promicanje

1540
00:59:45,820 --> 00:59:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] ljudskog i duhovnog razvitka

1541
00:59:47,260 --> 00:59:49,420
[SPEAKER_00] te oblažavanje siromaštva širom svijeta.

1542
00:59:49,960 --> 00:59:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] Po njegovoj zamisli, ove projekte treba voditi ženski ogranak.

1543
00:59:53,559 --> 00:59:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] Premda su u njemu bile samo tri članice,

1544
00:59:55,980 --> 00:59:59,320
[SPEAKER_00] a sve tri su živele u Madridu po haranom posljedice

1545
00:59:59,320 --> 01:00:00,719
[SPEAKER_00] Španjolskog građanskog rata.

1546
01:00:00,719 --> 01:00:03,940
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ima ekipu, njih tri.

1547
01:00:06,039 --> 01:00:08,159
[SPEAKER_00] Razbijem prozor, tamo pala je bomba.

1548
01:00:08,159 --> 01:00:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] Baš kruha nema,

1549
01:00:09,179 --> 01:00:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali eto, on skicira projekte.

1550
01:00:11,619 --> 01:00:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, ovo, kaže ovako,

1551
01:00:14,019 --> 01:00:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] i to opisuje Inkarnita Ortega,

1552
01:00:15,900 --> 01:00:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] jedna od njegovih tih prvih suradnica.

1553
01:00:17,500 --> 01:00:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] Otac Jose Maria položio je na stol

1554
01:00:19,739 --> 01:00:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] zemljovid na kojem su bili ucrtani

1555
01:00:21,420 --> 01:00:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] raznovrsni projekti,

1556
01:00:22,739 --> 01:00:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] što ih je ženski dio Opus Deja

1557
01:00:24,599 --> 01:00:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] trebao provesti u život u raznim dijelovima svijeta.

1558
01:00:27,420 --> 01:00:29,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se znam zaletiti,

1559
01:00:29,679 --> 01:00:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] onda me ovo tješi, još sam dobar.

1560
01:00:31,099 --> 01:00:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, već pri samu pokušaju

1561
01:00:34,340 --> 01:00:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] da pratim izlaganje Otca Jose Marije,

1562
01:00:36,539 --> 01:00:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] zavrtilo mi se u glavi.

1563
01:00:37,880 --> 01:00:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nam je sve ove projekte

1564
01:00:39,619 --> 01:00:41,179
[SPEAKER_00] objašnjala neobično potanko.

1565
01:00:41,179 --> 01:00:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, zamislim, njih tri para nema ništa.

1566
01:00:43,239 --> 01:00:45,780
[SPEAKER_00] On još iscrta kak će se živica,

1567
01:00:45,780 --> 01:00:46,760
[SPEAKER_00] vjeratno napraviti.

1568
01:00:46,760 --> 01:00:52,139
[SPEAKER_00] Gradnju poljoprivrednih škola za seljakilje.

1569
01:00:52,139 --> 01:00:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] Zatim, škola za različite vrste

1570
01:00:54,320 --> 01:00:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] profesionalne izobrazbe.

1571
01:00:55,719 --> 01:00:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] Studenski domovi.

1572
01:00:57,159 --> 01:00:59,659
[SPEAKER_00] Rodilišta u gradovima širom svijeta.

1573
01:00:59,659 --> 01:01:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] Uvođenje pokretnih biblioteka

1574
01:01:01,860 --> 01:01:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] koje će donosit vrijednoj

1575
01:01:03,500 --> 01:01:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] obrazovnom smislu korisno štivo

1576
01:01:05,300 --> 01:01:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] u najudaljenija sela.

1577
01:01:06,539 --> 01:01:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] Otvaranje knjižara.

1578
01:01:08,099 --> 01:01:10,440
[SPEAKER_00] I sad kaže, presavijajući polako

1579
01:01:10,440 --> 01:01:11,480
[SPEAKER_00] zemljovid rekao je,

1580
01:01:11,480 --> 01:01:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] na sve ovo može se reagirat na dva načina.

1581
01:01:14,500 --> 01:01:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan je da pomislimo kako je ovo prekrasan,

1582
01:01:18,420 --> 01:01:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali neostvariv san.

1583
01:01:20,000 --> 01:01:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] A drugi je pouzdati se u gospodina

1584
01:01:23,400 --> 01:01:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] i povjerovati da će nam on,

1585
01:01:25,940 --> 01:01:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] kada već to traži od nas,

1586
01:01:28,360 --> 01:01:31,260
[SPEAKER_00] pomoći u nastojanju da ovaj stan ostvarimo.

1587
01:01:31,260 --> 01:01:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] Nadam se da ćete vi reagirat na drugi način.

1588
01:01:35,099 --> 01:01:38,719
[SPEAKER_00] I sad dalje ovaj navodi svoji izvište,

1589
01:01:38,719 --> 01:01:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

1590
01:01:39,059 --> 01:01:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, tadašnja je stvarnost bila glad,

1591
01:01:41,340 --> 01:01:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] umor i malaksalost.

1592
01:01:42,800 --> 01:01:44,280
[SPEAKER_00] Neimaština i siromaštvo.

1593
01:01:44,280 --> 01:01:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] Uvjeti živote u Španjolskoj 42.

1594
01:01:46,500 --> 01:01:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] nipošto nisu bili povoljni

1595
01:01:48,320 --> 01:01:50,719
[SPEAKER_00] za ostvarenje tako ambicioznih snova.

1596
01:01:50,719 --> 01:01:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] Eskriva je, međutim,

1597
01:01:52,400 --> 01:01:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] bio ispunjen nadnaravnom nadom,

1598
01:01:54,199 --> 01:01:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] koja ga je neprekidno pokretala naprijed.

1599
01:01:57,340 --> 01:01:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] U godinama što su uslijedile,

1600
01:01:58,980 --> 01:02:01,480
[SPEAKER_00] ostvareni su svi projekti

1601
01:02:01,480 --> 01:02:03,159
[SPEAKER_00] koje je zamislio 1942.

1602
01:02:03,159 --> 01:02:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] E to je nada.

1603
01:02:05,099 --> 01:02:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] I to je nada koja proizlazi

1604
01:02:07,219 --> 01:02:08,300
[SPEAKER_00] izdruženja s Bogom,

1605
01:02:08,300 --> 01:02:09,699
[SPEAKER_00] kojom je sve moguće.

1606
01:02:09,699 --> 01:02:12,260
[SPEAKER_00] I one koju u srcu poznaje takvog Boga,

1607
01:02:12,260 --> 01:02:14,099
[SPEAKER_00] Bog radi kroz njega.

1608
01:02:14,099 --> 01:02:16,360
[SPEAKER_00] Može vani biti bombe,

1609
01:02:16,360 --> 01:02:17,519
[SPEAKER_00] neimaština,

1610
01:02:17,519 --> 01:02:18,280
[SPEAKER_00] glad,

1611
01:02:18,280 --> 01:02:19,679
[SPEAKER_00] malo ljudi,

1612
01:02:19,679 --> 01:02:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] ništa,

1613
01:02:20,300 --> 01:02:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali on zna kom je povjerno.

1614
01:02:24,039 --> 01:02:25,780
[SPEAKER_00] Već na dan njegove smrti

1615
01:02:25,780 --> 01:02:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] opust 9.000 članova

1616
01:02:28,199 --> 01:02:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] u preku 50 zemalja.

1617
01:02:30,960 --> 01:02:33,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zato li on zna o kom je povjerno?

1618
01:02:33,820 --> 01:02:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ljudi, mi služimo sve mogućem Bogu.

1619
01:02:36,239 --> 01:02:39,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj put koji stavljam sad pred vas

1620
01:02:39,219 --> 01:02:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] u ovoj godini

1621
01:02:40,559 --> 01:02:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] je jedinstvena prilika.

1622
01:02:43,380 --> 01:02:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] I vi možete na njega odgovoriti

1623
01:02:46,039 --> 01:02:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] na dva načina.

1624
01:02:46,840 --> 01:02:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ove tri su bile hrabre

1625
01:02:49,579 --> 01:02:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] i ostale su s njim.

1626
01:02:50,579 --> 01:02:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu ga smjestile.

1627
01:02:54,039 --> 01:02:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] u neku ustanovu.

1628
01:02:55,300 --> 01:02:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovdje ti ljudi nisu posebni.

1629
01:02:59,960 --> 01:03:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je Sveti Jan Pavao II. kaže

1630
01:03:01,880 --> 01:03:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] danas u 21. stoljeću

1631
01:03:04,159 --> 01:03:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] se svetost traži

1632
01:03:05,619 --> 01:03:06,900
[SPEAKER_00] od svakoga

1633
01:03:06,900 --> 01:03:07,699
[SPEAKER_00] i kod svakoga

1634
01:03:07,699 --> 01:03:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] i moguće je kod svakoga.

1635
01:03:09,079 --> 01:03:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Bernardi Sklervoa kaže

1636
01:03:11,659 --> 01:03:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje naziva ovu fazu sjedinjenja

1637
01:03:13,739 --> 01:03:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] supružnička ljubav.

1638
01:03:14,940 --> 01:03:16,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zaručnikovi prijatelji.

1639
01:03:16,820 --> 01:03:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] Univerzalna ljubav prema svima

1640
01:03:18,940 --> 01:03:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] čak i prema neprijateljima.

1641
01:03:20,880 --> 01:03:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] Znači navodi dvije

1642
01:03:22,460 --> 01:03:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] bliske, najintimnije veze.

1643
01:03:24,699 --> 01:03:26,260
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo, najintimnija,

1644
01:03:26,260 --> 01:03:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] to je supružnička ljubav.

1645
01:03:27,579 --> 01:03:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, duše već tako sjedinjenja

1646
01:03:29,960 --> 01:03:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] sa Bogom,

1647
01:03:30,900 --> 01:03:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] kao što su supružnici sjedinjeni,

1648
01:03:32,420 --> 01:03:34,039
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno trebali bi biti sjedinjeni.

1649
01:03:34,039 --> 01:03:36,480
[SPEAKER_00] A navodi se primjer

1650
01:03:36,480 --> 01:03:37,780
[SPEAKER_00] Zaručnikovi prijatelji.

1651
01:03:37,780 --> 01:03:39,280
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, da ne idem pre daleko

1652
01:03:39,280 --> 01:03:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] objašnjavanje,

1653
01:03:39,860 --> 01:03:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zaručnikov prijatelj je izraz

1654
01:03:41,460 --> 01:03:42,699
[SPEAKER_00] koji se koristio

1655
01:03:42,699 --> 01:03:44,280
[SPEAKER_00] u hebrijskom jeziku

1656
01:03:44,280 --> 01:03:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] za nekog ko je kum više.

1657
01:03:46,039 --> 01:03:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] I sjećate se ono kad

1658
01:03:47,420 --> 01:03:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] Svet Ivan Krstitelj kaže,

1659
01:03:49,460 --> 01:03:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] kad su ga pitali

1660
01:03:51,179 --> 01:03:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] da li on kriz kojima doći,

1661
01:03:52,340 --> 01:03:52,920
[SPEAKER_00] on je rekao da je on

1662
01:03:52,920 --> 01:03:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zaručnikov prijatelj

1663
01:03:53,960 --> 01:03:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] koji čuje Zaručnikov glas

1664
01:03:55,460 --> 01:03:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] i raduje se njemu.

1665
01:03:57,000 --> 01:03:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, je li znate

1666
01:03:58,619 --> 01:04:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] zašto se Zaručnikov prijatelj

1667
01:04:00,039 --> 01:04:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] radova Zaručnikov glasu?

1668
01:04:03,500 --> 01:04:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom,

1669
01:04:04,199 --> 01:04:06,219
[SPEAKER_00] Zaručnikov prijatelj je bio

1670
01:04:06,219 --> 01:04:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] puno bliskija veza

1671
01:04:07,500 --> 01:04:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] nego što su danas kumovi.

1672
01:04:08,820 --> 01:04:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] To znači,

1673
01:04:09,539 --> 01:04:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] to je bio neko s kim si odraso

1674
01:04:11,119 --> 01:04:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] i koji je znao

1675
01:04:12,380 --> 01:04:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] sve tvoje tajne,

1676
01:04:13,440 --> 01:04:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] kojom si se povjerao

1677
01:04:14,960 --> 01:04:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] za sve svoje muke,

1678
01:04:15,920 --> 01:04:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] sve svoje probleme

1679
01:04:17,059 --> 01:04:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] i bio ti je stvarno

1680
01:04:17,980 --> 01:04:18,800
[SPEAKER_00] jako blizak.

1681
01:04:18,800 --> 01:04:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] I onda,

1682
01:04:19,900 --> 01:04:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi zaslijedila

1683
01:04:21,280 --> 01:04:22,179
[SPEAKER_00] židovska svadba,

1684
01:04:22,179 --> 01:04:23,360
[SPEAKER_00] Zaručnikov prijatelj je bio

1685
01:04:23,360 --> 01:04:24,280
[SPEAKER_00] zadužen da sve

1686
01:04:24,280 --> 01:04:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] jako uveseljava,

1687
01:04:25,699 --> 01:04:26,260
[SPEAKER_00] podiže,

1688
01:04:26,260 --> 01:04:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo, napija ih

1689
01:04:27,480 --> 01:04:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] i sve ono što je trebalo napraviti.

1690
01:04:29,179 --> 01:04:30,179
[SPEAKER_00] To vidimo čak da Isusu

1691
01:04:30,179 --> 01:04:30,920
[SPEAKER_00] nije bilo problem

1692
01:04:30,920 --> 01:04:31,780
[SPEAKER_00] da prvo čudo

1693
01:04:31,780 --> 01:04:33,699
[SPEAKER_00] napravi da već

1694
01:04:33,699 --> 01:04:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] lagano pripito ekipu

1695
01:04:35,159 --> 01:04:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] dodatno napije

1696
01:04:36,019 --> 01:04:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] jer se za svadbi očekivalo

1697
01:04:37,519 --> 01:04:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] to potpuno veselje

1698
01:04:38,900 --> 01:04:40,219
[SPEAKER_00] i Zaručnikov prijatelj je bio

1699
01:04:40,219 --> 01:04:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] zadužen za to.

1700
01:04:41,119 --> 01:04:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] I sad,

1701
01:04:42,199 --> 01:04:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] ovo će nama zvučat čudno,

1702
01:04:44,400 --> 01:04:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali nismo u hebrerskoj tradiciji,

1703
01:04:45,940 --> 01:04:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi uslijedila prva bračna noć,

1704
01:04:47,659 --> 01:04:49,820
[SPEAKER_00] onda bi Zaručnikov prijatelj

1705
01:04:49,820 --> 01:04:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] ušao u ložnicu

1706
01:04:50,659 --> 01:04:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] zajedno sa Zaručnikom i Zaručnicom.

1707
01:04:53,119 --> 01:04:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da ne bi

1708
01:04:54,380 --> 01:04:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] tledao šta se događa,

1709
01:04:55,619 --> 01:04:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] nego je slušao.

1710
01:04:56,739 --> 01:05:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, ako je Zaručnica bila djevica,

1711
01:05:00,659 --> 01:05:02,739
[SPEAKER_00] onda je ovo je uskliknuo

1712
01:05:02,739 --> 01:05:05,219
[SPEAKER_00] i zato se Zaručnikov prijatelj

1713
01:05:05,219 --> 01:05:06,719
[SPEAKER_00] radova Zaručnikovu glasu,

1714
01:05:06,719 --> 01:05:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] na to je Ivan Krstelj mislio

1715
01:05:08,039 --> 01:05:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] i on bi otišao svim gostima

1716
01:05:11,199 --> 01:05:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao istina je

1717
01:05:12,199 --> 01:05:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je cura stvarno dobra,

1718
01:05:13,440 --> 01:05:14,579
[SPEAKER_00] nije se još nikom podjela,

1719
01:05:14,579 --> 01:05:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] brak je sklopljen i valjano.

1720
01:05:16,000 --> 01:05:19,360
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, zato Isus kaže

1721
01:05:19,360 --> 01:05:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno Ivan Krstelj

1722
01:05:21,159 --> 01:05:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] da je on Zaručnikov prijatelj.

1723
01:05:22,760 --> 01:05:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da kad čujete to evanđelje

1724
01:05:24,980 --> 01:05:26,260
[SPEAKER_00] da znate objasniti šta je.

1725
01:05:26,739 --> 01:05:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] Univerzalna ljubav prema svima

1726
01:05:33,920 --> 01:05:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] čak i prema neprijateljima.

1727
01:05:36,039 --> 01:05:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, tu je iz te čvrste,

1728
01:05:38,420 --> 01:05:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] znači, sjedinjujuće ljubavi s Bogom,

1729
01:05:40,920 --> 01:05:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] koju Sveti Bernal uspoređuje

1730
01:05:43,179 --> 01:05:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] baš tom supružničkom

1731
01:05:44,340 --> 01:05:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] ili tom bliskom prijateljskom ljubavlju,

1732
01:05:46,119 --> 01:05:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] se javlja ljubav prema svima

1733
01:05:48,320 --> 01:05:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] čak i prema neprijateljima.

1734
01:05:49,699 --> 01:05:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] To vidimo kad Svetijan pavao drugi

1735
01:05:51,460 --> 01:05:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi i oprašta i moli

1736
01:05:53,659 --> 01:05:56,139
[SPEAKER_00] za čovjeka koji ga je pokušao ubiti.

1737
01:05:56,139 --> 01:05:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] I vidimo da je to stvarno iskreno,

1738
01:05:57,619 --> 01:05:58,780
[SPEAKER_00] da to nije glumljen čin.

1739
01:05:59,739 --> 01:06:01,800
[SPEAKER_00] Mene je šokiralo, sjećam se kad sam bio djete,

1740
01:06:01,800 --> 01:06:04,280
[SPEAKER_00] moja obitelj počeo u ovoj strani,

1741
01:06:04,280 --> 01:06:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo Bakina obitelji,

1742
01:06:05,619 --> 01:06:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] izrazito bila pobožna i predana

1743
01:06:07,579 --> 01:06:09,739
[SPEAKER_00] i stvarno istrpila veliki progon

1744
01:06:09,739 --> 01:06:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] u vrijeme komunizma.

1745
01:06:10,739 --> 01:06:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] I od Bakine sestre, sin Marino,

1746
01:06:14,360 --> 01:06:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg sam joj dobro i poznava,

1747
01:06:15,440 --> 01:06:17,360
[SPEAKER_00] moj bratić je tragično stradao,

1748
01:06:17,360 --> 01:06:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] bio u Koreji kao pomorac,

1749
01:06:18,880 --> 01:06:20,659
[SPEAKER_00] ubio ga jedan Filipinac,

1750
01:06:20,659 --> 01:06:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] baš zato jer je taj dan dobio plaću

1751
01:06:22,619 --> 01:06:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] i ubio ga je doslovce zbog, ne znam,

1752
01:06:24,440 --> 01:06:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] tisuću, dvije, tisuće dolara

1753
01:06:25,880 --> 01:06:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] i uzeo mu to, išli su negdje na piću,

1754
01:06:29,019 --> 01:06:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj vidio da je on dobio plaću

1755
01:06:30,320 --> 01:06:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] i proboga iza sa tankim nožem onim

1756
01:06:32,460 --> 01:06:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] i ovaj je na mjestu umro 22 godine.

1757
01:06:34,380 --> 01:06:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] Treba se drugi dan vratiti.

1758
01:06:36,039 --> 01:06:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je stvarno potreslo cijelu našu obitelj.

1759
01:06:38,239 --> 01:06:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ovo što je meni kod djete

1760
01:06:39,900 --> 01:06:41,360
[SPEAKER_00] još jače potreslo tad,

1761
01:06:41,360 --> 01:06:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] je to što je teta Ivanka,

1762
01:06:45,019 --> 01:06:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] koja je i nače jako bila aktivna u crkvi

1763
01:06:46,840 --> 01:06:47,559
[SPEAKER_00] i stvarno je,

1764
01:06:47,559 --> 01:06:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] i dok su živjeli u Čikagu

1765
01:06:50,139 --> 01:06:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] i sad dok su živjeli ovdje u Hrvatskoj,

1766
01:06:52,440 --> 01:06:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] bila predana Bogu.

1767
01:06:54,320 --> 01:06:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom trenu, i to dosta,

1768
01:06:55,579 --> 01:06:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] nije prošlo puno vremena od tog,

1769
01:06:57,519 --> 01:07:00,579
[SPEAKER_00] rekla je, ja sam oprostila tom čovjeku,

1770
01:07:00,579 --> 01:07:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] posvojit kao svog sina

1771
01:07:02,539 --> 01:07:04,840
[SPEAKER_00] i da će do kraja života molit za njega.

1772
01:07:04,840 --> 01:07:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam, tad nisam mogo vjerovati

1773
01:07:07,420 --> 01:07:08,360
[SPEAKER_00] kako je to moguće.

1774
01:07:08,360 --> 01:07:10,300
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo svi bili puni bijesa tada

1775
01:07:10,300 --> 01:07:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] i možete misliti ono kako je,

1776
01:07:12,079 --> 01:07:14,719
[SPEAKER_00] ali ona stvarno nije nikad to više spomenula.

1777
01:07:14,719 --> 01:07:17,579
[SPEAKER_00] I to je već ova univerzalna ljubav

1778
01:07:17,579 --> 01:07:19,679
[SPEAKER_00] prema svima, čak i prema neprijateljima.

1779
01:07:19,679 --> 01:07:23,340
[SPEAKER_00] I sveti Franjo Saleški kaže ovako,

1780
01:07:23,340 --> 01:07:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] upravljan ljubavlju,

1781
01:07:24,800 --> 01:07:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] supružnička ljubav,

1782
01:07:26,199 --> 01:07:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] savršeno sjedinjenje volja u vršenju zapovjedi,

1783
01:07:29,059 --> 01:07:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] prihvaćenju savjeta i poticaja duha svetoga.

1784
01:07:32,000 --> 01:07:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] Isus živi u nama i po nama,

1785
01:07:34,179 --> 01:07:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] savršena ljubav izgoni strah,

1786
01:07:36,099 --> 01:07:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali motivi vezani u strahu od kazne i traženja nagrade

1787
01:07:39,519 --> 01:07:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] da još su uvijek prisutni u vrijeme kušnje.

1788
01:07:41,880 --> 01:07:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači još uvijek se to javlja u vrijeme kušnje

1789
01:07:44,380 --> 01:07:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] i nas Bog stavlja na kušnju

1790
01:07:46,159 --> 01:07:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] da bi tu našu ljubav dovao do savršenstva.

1791
01:07:48,980 --> 01:07:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] I Filotea je zapravo prvo dijelo

1792
01:07:50,619 --> 01:07:52,360
[SPEAKER_00] koje je baš bilo napisano za lajk.

1793
01:07:52,360 --> 01:07:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Franjo Saleški je počeo

1794
01:07:54,300 --> 01:07:55,760
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno se,

1795
01:07:55,760 --> 01:07:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] započeo je to posvećenje lajka.

1796
01:07:59,079 --> 01:07:59,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali prije,

1797
01:07:59,840 --> 01:08:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo prije 20. stoljeća

1798
01:08:02,400 --> 01:08:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] se stvarno vjerovalo da je taj uzvišeni

1799
01:08:04,199 --> 01:08:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] sveti život stvarno samo za redovnike.

1800
01:08:07,400 --> 01:08:09,880
[SPEAKER_00] Zato su se oni jedini i mogli pričešćivati svaki dan.

1801
01:08:09,880 --> 01:08:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, 20. stoljeća,

1802
01:08:11,599 --> 01:08:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] a pogotovo da je s prvo stoljeća

1803
01:08:13,119 --> 01:08:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] o što nas je uveo sveti Ivan Pavl II.

1804
01:08:14,860 --> 01:08:20,819
[SPEAKER_00] nam donosi ovo iskustvo novo.

1805
01:08:20,819 --> 01:08:25,359
[SPEAKER_00] I na vama je da se pokrenete.

1806
01:08:25,359 --> 01:08:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] Završit ću sa tekstom

1807
01:08:26,579 --> 01:08:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ivana Pavla II.

1808
01:08:28,619 --> 01:08:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg citira Ralf Martin.

1809
01:08:30,460 --> 01:08:31,979
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže ovako,

1810
01:08:31,979 --> 01:08:33,979
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što nas doista spričava da se velikodušno

1811
01:08:33,979 --> 01:08:36,659
[SPEAKER_00] odazovemo Isusovu pozivu,

1812
01:08:37,260 --> 01:08:39,439
[SPEAKER_00] Pozivu II. Vatikanskog sabora

1813
01:08:39,439 --> 01:08:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] i opetovanim poticajima duha svetoga

1814
01:08:41,619 --> 01:08:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] nisu vanjske okolnosti

1815
01:08:43,460 --> 01:08:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] naših života,

1816
01:08:46,199 --> 01:08:49,560
[SPEAKER_00] nego nutarnja tromos naših crdaca.

1817
01:08:49,560 --> 01:08:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] Mora nam biti jasno

1818
01:08:51,239 --> 01:08:52,979
[SPEAKER_00] da nikad neće doći bolje vrijeme

1819
01:08:52,979 --> 01:08:54,939
[SPEAKER_00] ili bolji sklop okolnosti

1820
01:08:54,939 --> 01:08:55,819
[SPEAKER_00] nego što je sada,

1821
01:08:55,819 --> 01:08:58,659
[SPEAKER_00] kako bismo odgovorili pozivu na svetost.

1822
01:08:58,659 --> 01:09:01,579
[SPEAKER_00] Tko zna koliko ćemo živjeti na ovoj zemlji?

1823
01:09:01,579 --> 01:09:03,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znamo ni koliko ćemo dugo živjeti

1824
01:09:03,899 --> 01:09:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] ni što budućnost nosi.

1825
01:09:05,500 --> 01:09:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] Sada je najprikladnije vrijeme.

1826
01:09:07,659 --> 01:09:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] Same stvari za koje mislimo da su prepreke

1827
01:09:11,199 --> 01:09:14,199
[SPEAKER_00] tek su sredstva koja nam Bog daje

1828
01:09:14,199 --> 01:09:17,020
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi nas privukao da se dublje pouzda mun.

1829
01:09:18,520 --> 01:09:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] sada je vrijeme.

1830
01:09:19,619 --> 01:09:22,300
[SPEAKER_00] Što kaže psalam, sada je dan spasa.

1831
01:09:22,300 --> 01:09:26,140
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ono što mislite da vas sad do toga odvraća

1832
01:09:26,140 --> 01:09:28,840
[SPEAKER_00] su samo one okolnosti kojom je Bog dao

1833
01:09:28,840 --> 01:09:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] da u njima postignete svetost.

1834
01:09:31,739 --> 01:09:35,560
[SPEAKER_00] One koji su prepreke često nas još dublje

1835
01:09:35,560 --> 01:09:36,979
[SPEAKER_00] bacaju Bogu u ruke.

1836
01:09:36,979 --> 01:09:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] I zato jas pozivam stvarno da svi zajedno

1837
01:09:40,579 --> 01:09:43,300
[SPEAKER_00] odemo na putovanje kroz ovu godinu.

1838
01:09:43,300 --> 01:09:45,479
[SPEAKER_00] Biće i gostiju, malo ćemo se odmoli

1839
01:09:45,479 --> 01:09:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] da ne bude previše mistike,

1840
01:09:46,819 --> 01:09:49,779
[SPEAKER_00] ali uglavnom do oživka ćemo proći sve ove faze

1841
01:09:49,779 --> 01:09:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] i vjerujem ako duhom uđete u to, uživaćete.

1842
01:09:52,619 --> 01:09:53,979
[SPEAKER_00] Navući ćete se.

1843
01:09:53,979 --> 01:09:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

